          "id": "x-joshwoodward-2026-07-16-p2-s0",
          "text": "We just released our first-ever Gemini Southeast Asia Report (below), 3 insights: 1/ Active users more than doubled in the last year 2/ 70% of prompts are submitted in native languages 3/ 40% of prompts only use voice, image, or video Gemini's local language + multimodal capabilities + mobile apps are driving growth, and we have more coming soon for the region! 🇮🇩🇲🇾🇵🇭🇸🇬🇹🇭🇻🇳",
